00:00:10.980 --> 00:00:12.300
sebanyak mungkin mitos komputasi kuantum

5
00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:15.720
dalam enam puluh detik.

6
00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:19.640
Komputer kuantum itu benar-benar nyata,

7
00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:24.460
